The accolades keeping pouring in for Trevor Noah. In yet another massive notch on his belt TIME magazine has named the host of The Daily Show as a next generation leader. Since his debut in 2015 the South African comedian has more than doubled the show s international reach and he has now become the master of the eloquent Trump-takedown said TIME on Instagram.TIME named 10 young people who they believe are leaving a mark in various sectors including arts entertainment sports and business.https://www.instagram.com/time/